<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="aboard-adv">aboard <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ə'bɔːd/    美 /ə'bɔːrd/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-on-board">1.★ <strong>在船 / 车 / 飞机上; 上船 / 车 / 飞机 (on board)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The plane crashed, killing all 200 people aboard. 
飞机失事，机上200人全部遇难。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The train's about to leave. <strong>All aboard</strong>!
火车即将离站，请所有乘客上车！</p></div></div>